title: 210: 10 Takeaways from Week 3
itunes:title: 210: 10 Takeaways from Week 3
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down the biggest takeaways from this past week's slate of games. Was the Falcons vs. Lions thriller a playoff preview? Will Kareem Hunt run away with the rookie of the year award? How did the Bears beat the Steelers? All that and much more from Week 3.
